Patch 1 for version 7.7 - 14 July 2024

Changes
=======
1) Ignore button UP events in the STANDARD and ALTERNATIVE rotary classes
2) Correct menu step through not working if alarm feature set
3) Driver for the Grove v5 RGB I2C LCD added (lcd_i2c_jhd1313_sgm31323.py)

Also see README file 

To install the patch
====================
cd /usr/share/radio
wget http://www.bobrathbone.com/raspberrypi/packages/radiod-patch-7.7-1.tar.gz
tar -xvf radiod-patch-7.7-1.tar.gz

This patch contains all previous patches unless patch 1.

